prodNameC: 拜爾斯達光學免疫法流感病毒測定試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Sample Diluent-4.1 mL:
0.85% NaCl
Reagent 1-4.1 mL:
Specimen Extraction Reagent, pH 7.0 buffer solution containing surfactant and reducing agent.
Reagent 2-1.2 mL:
Conjugate, pH 7.2 buffer solution containing surfactant, stabilizing proteins, and anti influenza A and B antibodies (mouse) each conjugated to Horseradish Peroxidase (HRP).
Wash-115 mL:
pH 7.2 phosphate buffer containing surfactant
Substrate-2.0 mL:
pH5.5 aqueous solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) and hydrogen peroxide.

Positive Control-0.7 mL:
Formaldehyde-inactivated influenza A virus (A/Hong Kong/68 (H3N2) suspension in a buffered protein solution
Negative Control-0.7 mL:
Buffered protein solution.
Test Devices-30 ea.:
Surface coated with a mixture of anti-influenza A and B antibodies (mouse).
Transfer Pipettes - 30 ea.
Extraction Tubes - 30 ea.
Swabs- 30 ea. :
Sterile Rayon swabs.
applicantAddr: 新北市永和區中山路一段174號11樓
efficacy: 定性偵測流感病毒之抗原。
